CAREjourney.com is revolutionizing in home care by offering personalized tools and resources that narrow and tailor the caregiving search. The end result is a CAREJourneyâ„¢ that meets your caring needs. The beta version of CAREjourney.com has launched providing the opportunity for care providers and care seekers to connect with one another. Similar to a date matching site, CAREjourney matches CareGivers to Care Receivers based upon needs, experience, interest, and personality. Other community benefits for members include blogs, forums, and education for both family and professional caregivers. CAREjourney.com specializes in elder care or senior in home care, and those with well special needs while serving as a job resource for caregivers.
